The following message is carved into the stone.  It seems to have been here for ages, because the letters are quite faint.

"Wary be ye who ennterre yon darke woode.  'Tis foll of the blackest of majicks and foulest of creeturs!  Ye be warned!"
Place this object in any area where you want tracking to occur.  Set Will to the DC of tracking in this area.
